tool_description: Data for Youtube, Spotify music videos, tracks, albums, artist & more
name: MusicData API
title: MusicData API

api_list.name: /youtube/global/{countryID}/{timeframe}
api_list.description: Weekly/Daily country Youtube chart for a specific country. Read external docs for more information
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://musicdata-api.p.rapidapi.com/youtube/global/kr/daily"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "musicdata-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
